reviews.review_text:
this doesn't sound better to me? I really appreciate the effort by EVERYBODY who takes the time to transfer these sources... However, this one doesn't sound right to me ... I have previous transfers of this source and it doesn't sound like this ... this source leans heavy on one side, and sounds rather muffled ... 

how bout this , just buy the commercial release ... it sounds the best I've ever heard of this show ... and it's not from Betty's "personal" reels... many of her soundboards were not "perfect" by any means ...

donnie l Aren't the official release a cleanup of Betty's board? If not where does this recording come from?

And Cornell is no way the best GD concert! And not in 77 too!
I was an annoying 8 year old when this occurred.
